Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:23.07,Honorifics - Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A brave heart and incredible deductions,\Na rhythm that jumps to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.07,Honorifics - Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Spinning the potter's wheel in ceramics class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:26.87,Honorifics - Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Pay close attention to the words on the cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.27,0:00:28.91,Honorifics - Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.44,Honorifics - Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A kid with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.61,Honorifics - Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is... Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:46.99,Title,Sign,0,0,0,,The Murderous Pottery Class\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kyoku Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:56.83,Signs,Note,0,0,0,,Note: Kyoku Shin is one of the most violent\Nand full contact forms of karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that you're starting karate, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:02:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look closer! It says Makoto Kyougoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made this during the pottery class that you just joined, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sonoko, isn't it too small for Kyougoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's because that one is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one is for Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:26.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's so big...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did you write your name on it, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person I love is out in distant lands exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I get stuck here waiting for his rare calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is why I, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}, made this cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it will be hard not to remember me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sonoko, didn't you send him the handmade\Nsweater that you bought from that store?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that? No I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like you told me, I shouldn't cheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, even if I put all my effort into knitting that sweater\Nmyself, he would only wear it in the winter anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this! He'll be using it every day, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although there is one thing that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm scared that some woman will take advantage of Makoto's kindness and seduce him into going out with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:21.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the number of people like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seduce others and make them fall in love with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, how worried I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.19,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What an awful person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:40.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In order to run away from the punishments for his crimes, he killed himself without thinking about his now widowed wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:43.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:55.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ma'am, if my heart can comfort you, then I will lend it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't worry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:12.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But Detective, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.90,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Sonoko. You said that you attend\Na pottery class on Sundays, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why? Are you interested in it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:40.73,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Three Weeks Later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, good work. Yours looks very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:56.84,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Muneyuki Mino (62)\NCraftsman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad that great pottery is wasted with those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do they mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:05:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, uh... they have no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so. Well, good luck then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you write on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a secret, secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know! You're going to write\N"I Love Shinichi" on it, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you one of the student's kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does anyone know this child?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't happen to follow us, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-ojisan{\r} asked me to come check up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird, Dad came here himself last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} asked this\Nboy to follow and check up on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make sure that you're not cheating on him, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheating!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:06:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it! Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r} would never do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your face tells me that you're being paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, how much is he paying you? 100 yen? 200 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:16.59,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Kikuyo Kasama (29)\NMuneyuki's Assistant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since you are here already...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say boy, why don't you try molding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mind, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not. Let's see what he can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've met Kikuemon{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.00,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Potter Kikuemon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we learned a bunch of things from his assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. That's why you're learning so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How amazing! Meeting him, a human treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he invited my dad to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a murder, but Ran's dad\Nwas easily able to solve that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Solve a murder? Could your father be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father didn't say anything when he came last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the daughter of Mouri Kogoro, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard of him. He's called Sleeping Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a huge fan of his!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like this place is packed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh you're back, Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came as soon as I finished work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:27.16,Character Card,Sign,0,0,0,,Mino Moto (31)\NBusinessman (Muneyuki's inheritor)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, father... I'll change my clothes and come help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Insurance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you forced to get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, father asked me to get it. I don't know\Nwhy, but he asked me to get it just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if he's hoping it would help his pottery business, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After his daughter died, he suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now he's just another pathetic drunk who\Nlikes to fiddle around with pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so cold towards your departed wife,\NMiss "Everlasting Love", and her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What good is "Everlasting Love" now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to get close to the old man,\Ntake his money, and then divorce her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't last long, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it is fine isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His life is almost over because of his constant drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and after his death, we'll sell this\Nold dump and open our own new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll make a fortune if we sell those "Sleeping Works".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, who did you put down as your inheritor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, who else? My one and only girl, that's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, could you die for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kikuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I'll take care of the furnace. Would\Nyou please go back and check up on my students?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, is this neck tie new?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Kikuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gave it to me yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told her beige wouldn't look good on me, but she kept insisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would look great around your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran. Show it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Sonoko.\NEveryone will see it after you're done anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, did it break?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.36,0:09:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it from the storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do know what I will do to you if you look at it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my hand slipped and I dropped a plate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you, but could you clean this up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like there was something sharp in the clay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pieces of the broken plate probably got on my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let me get you the first aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the top right shelf in the closet room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:52.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, please hurry and get it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be careful when you're doing pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fingers are the most important things potters have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, any idea where Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is?\NI haven't seen him for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not at the furnace either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only place left is this storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't possibly be here! The only place someone\Ncan hide in here is in the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I opened that closet when I got the first aid kit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I didn't see anyone inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:40.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! At the bottom of the closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this an apron for the pottery class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right. It has the same pattern as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, showing part of his clothes while he is hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, hide and seek is over, Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll open it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, go call an ambulance immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, you better call the police too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our victim's name was Mino Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\N31 years old, and a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was he a student in this pottery class?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, he is the inheritor to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was married to my daughter, who died 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm this class's teacher, Mino Muneyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my assistant, Kasama Kikuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind describing the events before\Nyou realized that he was missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We lost track of him at around 5 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he was going to change his clothes, put on an apron, then come help us in class like he usually does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Kikuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. We searched for him everywhere, but we couldn't\Nfind him. This storage room was the only place left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when Sensei opened the closet, he was inside it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His Body... Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you found him... This isn't hide and seek,\Nand you normally wouldn't check in a closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course we would! Part of his apron was sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apron?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His apron was sticking out from the\Ncloset's lower, right-hand corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know how long it had been sticking out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall... When we were cleaning the shards of the broken dish next to the closet, it wasn't sticking out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Broken dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A plate fell in front of the closet a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These students rushed here, after hearing\Nthe sound of something breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.58,0:14:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my memory serves me right, Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nwas there and was wearing his apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You were with the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. That closet contains the student's aprons, so\NMoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} always puts on his apron in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, his coat's there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are there several overalls to the left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're for the students to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While making pottery, aprons are not large\Nenough to cover all your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what were you doing with the victim alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was looking for Kikuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I found\Nher with Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked me to come\Nand help him change his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Sensei came in and asked me to take care of\Nthe students while he watched over the furnace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to the students, just as Sensei had asked me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Mino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, that means that you were alone with the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't possibly be suspecting me, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said, Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} had left the room before I dropped the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, had I killed him and hid his body in the closet, these\Nstudents would've noticed the apron sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:16:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, you could've opened the closet after the students\Nfinished cleaning, then stuck that part out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei went out to the furnace while we were cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time we finished and returned, he was\Nin the classroom with the other students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, he helped Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} make some pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, Sensei was with us until we found Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I don't think he had a chance to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. In other words, it happened after\NRan and the others finished cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer might have asked the victim\Nto come here, and then killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also could have killed him somewhere else, dragged\Nthe body here, and hid it in the closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Maybe Kikuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saw the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I cut my finger while working on some pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Kikuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went and got the first aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moments later, we started searching for Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't see anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where was that first aid kit located?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the upper, right-hand corner of that closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! You opened the closet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but there was nobody inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, judging by the marks on the victim's neck,\Nthe murder weapon must've been this necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you find it odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would the criminal leave the necktie on the victim's neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too bad, that necktie was a present\Nfrom Kikuyo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:52.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You're mistaken. I didn't give him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? But he said that it was from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he said that, on his birthday, he found\Na gift with a congratulations note.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thought it was me being shy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Moto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was complaining about\Nsomething as I was leaving. He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Money makes people's hearts ruthless demons; even\Non my birthday, one of those demons might eat me."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A demon will eat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry Takagi. Verify that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... excuse me, but can anyone lend\Nme an ink pen? Mine is out of ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go get it, then. It must be in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are those scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't the police officer ask for an ink pen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm actually looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and look. My cup is almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well done, looks like you like pottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't like to stop in the middle of things, like that\Ndead man did. So, I want to finish it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop in the middle of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:39.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Didn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:43.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a difference in the length of his folded sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if... after he put his apron on and was getting\Nready, he was killed by someone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, boy, what if one of the sleeves was\Npulled on when he was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, then the criminal probably also pulled the necktie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Necktie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the pin on the necktie is so low.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you pull its end, then the tie would get bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't the pin too low?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he liked it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what if the difference in the sleeve\Nlength is something he liked as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you prefer everything to be symmetrical, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I noticed that, at the time the body\Nfell, you were standing to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then went to the left, just to make\Nup for the difference in length, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, the other time, when we noticed the apron sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:54.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That part of the apron was sticking out from the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd only open the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you opened both doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I preferred to open both doors at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my cup! Don't you think it's pretty good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... You really did a good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But boy, you seem to be a little confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're trying to hide something\Nbig, or you're facing a big decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, am I right? Because clay never lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, boy, you should think about your own problems\Nbefore you think about the problems of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who made this cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you were searching the drawers earlier,\NI took your cup and switched it with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd know the difference between the two cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if this is your cup, doesn't that mean\Nthat you're hiding something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, you're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
